data.description: The open and inviting traditional floor plan includes a welcoming interior which is bathed in natural light and combines a first-floor bedroom. Enjoy the sleek finishes in this ultra-modern kitchen that has been recently updated and features stainless-steel appliances and marble countertops. Equipped with lots of storage space, the cozy main bedroom affords a walk-in closet and scenic. Host a party in the beautifully maintained backyard, which features a covered patio as well as pineapple trees. The go-to spot for year-round fun. Just the suburban atmosphere you've been looking for! Wonderfully located in a relaxed Polk County neighborhood. Have plenty of room for vehicles and belongings in a useful single car attached garage. See for yourself what this home has to offer. Brand NEW fence, NEW garage doors, NEW stainless steel appliances, NEW marble countertops, NEW flooring, fresh paint on the exterior and interior, NEW water purifier system, and a NEW A/C system. Schedule a showing TODAY!
